rawplus_ex

rawplus_ex.Rd

Exposure (ex) data in rawplus format.

Usage

rawplus_ex

Format

a data frame with 4876 rows and 53 columns.

studyid

string Study Identifier

siteid

string Site Identifier

invid

string Investigator ID

scrnid

string Screen Identifier

subjid

string Subject Identifier

subjectid

string System Subject Identifier

datapagename

string eCRF Page Name

datapageid

string Internal ID for Data Page

foldername

string Folder Name

instancename

string Instance Name

recordid

string Record Identifier

record_dt

string Record Date

recordposition

float Record Position

mincreated_dts

string Earliest Data Creation Date/Time

maxupdated_dts

string Latest Data Update Date/Time

extrt

string Treatment Name

exds

string Actual Dose

exdsu

string Acutal Dose Units

exdsfrmn

int Number of Dose Form

exdsfrm

string Dose Form

exdsfrq

string Dosing Frequecy

exdsfrot

string Other Dosing Frequecy

exrte

string Route

exst_dt

string Start Date/Time of Treatment

exen_dt

string End Date/Time of Treatment

exongo

string EX Ongoing

experm

string Permanently Withdrawn

subjid_nsv

string SUBJECT IDENTIFIER

scrnid_nsv

string SCREENING IDENTIFIER

subjinit_nsv

string SUBJECT INITIALS

invid_nsv

string INVESTIGATOR ID

subject_nsv

string Subject name or identifier

instanceid_nsv

double Internal id for the instance

folder_nsv

string Folder OID

folderseq_nsv

double Folder sequence number

extrt_std_nsv

string Drug Name_Coded Value

exdstxt_nsv

double Dose per administration

exdosu_std_nsv

double Dose Units_Coded Value

exdsfrmn_raw_nsv

string Number of insert Dose Form (Tablets)_(Character)

exdosfrm_std_nsv

double Dose Form_Coded Value

exdosfrq_std_nsv

string Dosing Frequency_Coded Value

exroute_std_nsv

double Route_Coded Value

exrtoth_nsv

string EXRTOTH

exstdat_nsv

timestamp Start Date/Dose Date

exstdat_yy_nsv

double Start Date/Dose Date_Year

exstdat_mm_nsv

double Start Date/Dose Date_Month

exstdat_dd_nsv

double Start Date/Dose Date_Day

exendat_nsv

timestamp Stop Date

exendat_yy_nsv

double Stop Date_Year

exendat_mm_nsv

double Stop Date_Month

exendat_dd_nsv

double Stop Date_Day

exongo_std_nsv

string Check if Ongoing_Coded Value

experm_nsv

string if study drug was permanently withdrawn

Source

./data-raw/rawplus/ex.parquet
